This is just an experimental plugin for ConfirmEdit

sample:
Pick the correct Option Number
We pray to 1.Time 1.God 3.Lion 4.Tomato ?
 

Why Beneficial ?
* Bots don't have common sense
* No Images so loads faster
* Most Important - Good support for i18n
* Further plans to let the user just select the right option rather than typing text
This is a plugin for ConfirmEdit
To use add download the files to ConfirmEdit's folder and copy at the end of your LocalSettings.php
	require_once( "$IP/extensions/ConfirmEdit/MCQ.php"); 
	$wgCaptchaClass = 'MCQ';
	